{"tid":293238,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有黑警偽冒當事人　簽署驗傷同意書　被醫生識破","createTime":"2017-06-22T04:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T05:08:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"776fc3d2cbd120e65f88c25334c264bf8db29cff","tid":293238,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:13:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/ha-secrets-有警員偽冒當事人-簽署驗傷同意書/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fha-secrets-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%81%BD%E5%86%92%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E9%A9%97%E5%82%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%B8%2F&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=026e7be5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2Fha-secrets-%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%81%BD%E5%86%92%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B0%BD%E7%BD%B2%E9%A9%97%E5%82%B7%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E6%9B%B8%2F&h=4241512c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/ha-secrets-有警員偽冒當事人-簽署驗傷同意書/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police_9zi1Y_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice_9zi1Y_1200x0.png&h=f744da21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n供醫護人員匿名舉報醫院內幕消息的 Facebook 專頁「HA Secrets」（HA即醫管局），今日刊出一則消息指，有警員涉嫌在一間位於九龍的醫院，偽冒意識不清的當事人，簽署同意醫生向警方透露病情的驗傷同意書，被醫生當場識破，並影印該文件作記錄。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向醫管局及警方查詢，兩方均稱若無事發日期、醫院等資料，未能核實有關消息真偽。<br />\n<br />\nHA Secrets發佈的消息未有透露事發具體地點，僅稱是「九龍區某醫院急症室」，亦未披露事發日期，指「早排」有病人在半昏迷狀態下送院，負責警員要求醫生簽署驗傷文件，上有聲稱為病人自行簽署同意醫生披露傷勢的簽名，但負責醫生質疑，病人處於半昏迷狀態，不可能自行簽署，質疑警員冒簽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/wmut9n1xv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fwmut9n1xv%2Fimage.jpg&h=ff9c73f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「HA Secrets」早前曾刊出醫護人員披露，民建聯議員譚耀宗及陳恒鑌，分別在公立醫院「打尖」進行割瘜肉手術，及要求九龍西醫院接收太太跨區分娩。譚耀宗最終就事件道歉，陳恒鑌則否認事涉「特事特辦」。"},{"pid":"6c44e0c941a4769b1c71697ca05b6ee6abbcfafe","tid":293238,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"唔通係九龍灣果單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048805fb299f50061982dafb30a3fe7b7629c0c9","tid":293238,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e75c5f74ac7c3d4255827b11d3a2b3e9689f4341","tid":293238,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6a6469f1a84cd20a49dc10936397eeea3db2a435","tid":293238,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"偽造文書? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  違返私隱條例? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詐騙? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 革職入冊cut長糧? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c21d410dd3b42e0909b3a7295d3c34d2133b81a","tid":293238,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>偽造文書? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  違返私隱條例? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詐騙? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 革職入冊cut長糧? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗下就算啦<br />\n現實冇人告"},{"pid":"a282a0d5d8d2deb39a34519b07b2e8adf886a807","tid":293238,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=947100498745338&amp;id=731331330322257&amp;pnref=story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D947100498745338%26id%3D731331330322257%26pnre